    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1277480/extras/3fe4124ae87a539173befc60f0537bdb.poster.avif?t=1647963637\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1277480/extras/3fe4124ae87a539173befc60f0537bdb.webm?t=1647963637\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1277480/extras/3fe4124ae87a539173befc60f0537bdb.mp4?t=1647963637\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The Shepherd is a 2D, single-player game that combines RPG elements with a unique blended time-based turn-based battle system. Set in the deserts of Saudi Arabia.<br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >key Features</h2> </strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Protect your sheep from predators</strong> in turn-based battles where your attacks are made using a unique time-based bar mechanic that minimizes your dependence on luck. Each of these predators has their own special attacks and abilities. <br><br></li><li><strong>Feed your sheep</strong> as they roam around the grassland eating grass patches they encounter, or if they’re lucky stumbling upon special flowers which increase their stats. Once the sheep have been fed, you can shave off their wool to sell in the market. <br><br></li><li><strong>Buy and upgrade your weapons</strong> to help you defeat stronger predators. Each weapon has a different battle bar that can be enhanced with upgrades.<br><br></li><li><strong>Strengthen your sheep </strong> by increasing their core stats of beauty, fertility and agility.<br><br></li><li><strong>Breed your sheep</strong> to make various genetic combinations each with their own appearance and attributes.<br><br></li><li><strong>Meet variety of desert-folk</strong>  and help them with their problems. Help them and they will help you back with gifts, some helpful advice, and some not so helpful advice.<br><br></li><li><strong>Find the 6 mystic wells</strong> by seeking out the maps that will lead to them. When your sheep drink from these wells you will be able to select special upgrades for them. Unique to each bread.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2></li></ul>",
